parameters.name: ELTL1: Electron Low Telescope 1
parameters.description:
This column contains electron flux from Electrons Low (100-308            
                               keV) Spin Averages Telescope 1. Flux units are                            
                               electrons/(s cm^2 sr).

parameters.name: EHTL1: Electron High Telescope 1
parameters.description:
This column contains electron flux from Electrons High (E > 180           
                               keV) Spin Averages Telescope 1. Flux units are                            
                               electrons/(s cm^2 sr).
